{"tid":2132694,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"問女仔心態，化妝比異性睇","createTime":"2020-07-30T13:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T03:44:16.000Z","uid":204047,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a31386e081dad11641d99266f654e10126230bcb","tid":2132694,"uid":204047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"我女友平時見客出街都會化妝，但如果一啲普通同好熟既女仔fd聚會佢好少化妝<br />\n<br />\n但尋日佢化妝去一啲有男仔fd喺度既聚會，就引發左一啲問題<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得點解佢要化妝出去，佢就話想靚啲，咁我心態覺得你係咪化俾邊個睇呀，佢就話個兩個男仔fd你都見過啦 你懷疑啲咩<br />\n<br />\n想問下女仔化妝俾異性睇係咪正常？我太多心？"},{"pid":"88447bc06859487e12120799aa62734bae30c069","tid":2132694,"uid":104502,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"想自己靚啲都唔得？<br />\n你去啲有女嘅聚會 又污糟邋遢咁去？"},{"pid":"d12d7ac234d46d3f1b36a712a2fa1ff8e806ebcf","tid":2132694,"uid":55502,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"唔正常  建議分手"},{"pid":"a996ac92ae0b8379cfaa49945c648f7e26b79d91","tid":2132694,"uid":307907,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"化妝見人係尊重場合"},{"pid":"26e56d6dabeba54f1adcdd232f12feb877f69412","tid":2132694,"uid":8308,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"你自己問下自己 如果同行有女既 <br />\n你都會執靚d gel好頭 燙好衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516bced0b80bc92d732d5b5f91192de7c7348f4a","tid":2132694,"uid":277403,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"唔熟嘅先會化 費事冇晒形象姐"},{"pid":"4ff6a485ecc2d26e0adcfe9486e9f9d986e328cb","tid":2132694,"uid":163959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"女人天生就係貪靚<br />\n着靚啲都唔比 做男人有無咁自悲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428bbf0e934c5b82815db9393a1ae27c369d6c29","tid":2132694,"uid":238767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:08:59.000Z",